{
  "video_id": "s6rJLXq1Re0",
  "title": "How to read the genome and build a human being | Riccardo Sabatini",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12612.0,
      "end_time": 15374.0,
      "text": "For the next 16 minutes, I&#39;m going to take you on a journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15398.0,
      "end_time": 18484.0,
      "text": "that is probably the biggest dream of humanity:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18508.0,
      "end_time": 20523.0,
      "text": "to understand the code of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21720.0,
      "end_time": 23814.0,
      "text": "So for me, everything started many, many years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23839.0,
      "end_time": 26561.0,
      "text": "when I met the first 3D printer."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26586.0,
      "end_time": 28259.0,
      "text": "The concept was fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28284.0,
      "end_time": 30305.0,
      "text": "A 3D printer needs three elements:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30330.0,
      "end_time": 34464.0,
      "text": "a bit of information, some raw material, some energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34488.0,
      "end_time": 37822.0,
      "text": "and it can produce any object that was not there before."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38517.0,
      "end_time": 40654.0,
      "text": "I was doing physics, I was coming back home"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40678.0,
      "end_time": 44116.0,
      "text": "and I realized that I actually always knew a 3D printer."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44140.0,
      "end_time": 45476.0,
      "text": "And everyone does."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45500.0,
      "end_time": 46658.0,
      "text": "It was my mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46682.0,
      "end_time": 47683.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47707.0,
      "end_time": 50121.0,
      "text": "My mom takes three elements:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50145.0,
      "end_time": 54118.0,
      "text": "a bit of information, which is between my father and my mom in this case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54142.0,
      "end_time": 58299.0,
      "text": "raw elements and energy in the same media, that is food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58323.0,
      "end_time": 60831.0,
      "text": "and after several months, produces me."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60855.0,
      "end_time": 62666.0,
      "text": "And I was not existent before."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62691.0,
      "end_time": 66453.0,
      "text": "So apart from the shock of my mom discovering that she was a 3D printer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66477.0,
      "end_time": 71215.0,
      "text": "I immediately got mesmerized by that piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71239.0,
      "end_time": 72956.0,
      "text": "the first one, the information."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72980.0,
      "end_time": 75231.0,
      "text": "What amount of information does it take"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75255.0,
      "end_time": 77191.0,
      "text": "to build and assemble a human?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77215.0,
      "end_time": 78789.0,
      "text": "Is it much? Is it little?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78813.0,
      "end_time": 80993.0,
      "text": "How many thumb drives can you fill?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81170.0,
      "end_time": 83640.0,
      "text": "Well, I was studying physics at the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83665.0,
      "end_time": 89262.0,
      "text": "and I took this approximation of a human as a gigantic Lego piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89286.0,
      "end_time": 93710.0,
      "text": "So, imagine that the building blocks are little atoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93950.0,
      "end_time": 97748.0,
      "text": "and there is a hydrogen here, a carbon here, a nitrogen here."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97772.0,
      "end_time": 99343.0,
      "text": "So in the first approximation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99367.0,
      "end_time": 103710.0,
      "text": "if I can list the number of atoms that compose a human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103734.0,
      "end_time": 105121.0,
      "text": "I can build it."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105145.0,
      "end_time": 107173.0,
      "text": "Now, you can run some numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107198.0,
      "end_time": 110475.0,
      "text": "and that happens to be quite an astonishing number."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110499.0,
      "end_time": 113256.0,
      "text": "So the number of atoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113280.0,
      "end_time": 118350.0,
      "text": "the file that I will save in my thumb drive to assemble a little baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118590.0,
      "end_time": 122726.0,
      "text": "will actually fill an entire Titanic of thumb drives --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122750.0,
      "end_time": 125468.0,
      "text": "multiplied 2,000 times."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125957.0,
      "end_time": 129358.0,
      "text": "This is the miracle of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129382.0,
      "end_time": 131994.0,
      "text": "Every time you see from now on a pregnant lady,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132180.0,
      "end_time": 134874.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s assembling the biggest amount of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134898.0,
      "end_time": 136454.0,
      "text": "that you will ever encounter."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136478.0,
      "end_time": 139428.0,
      "text": "Forget big data, forget anything you heard of."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139452.0,
      "end_time": 142333.0,
      "text": "This is the biggest amount of information that exists."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142357.0,
      "end_time": 146190.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146214.0,
      "end_time": 150858.0,
      "text": "But nature, fortunately, is much smarter than a young physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150882.0,
      "end_time": 154458.0,
      "text": "and in four billion years, managed to pack this information"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154482.0,
      "end_time": 157187.0,
      "text": "in a small crystal we call DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157605.0,
      "end_time": 161917.0,
      "text": "We met it for the first time in 1950 when Rosalind Franklin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161941.0,
      "end_time": 163497.0,
      "text": "an amazing scientist, a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163521.0,
      "end_time": 164910.0,
      "text": "took a picture of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164934.0,
      "end_time": 170122.0,
      "text": "But it took us more than 40 years to finally poke inside a human cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170146.0,
      "end_time": 171748.0,
      "text": "take out this crystal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171772.0,
      "end_time": 174852.0,
      "text": "unroll it, and read it for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 175615.0,
      "end_time": 178856.0,
      "text": "The code comes out to be a fairly simple alphabet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 178880.0,
      "end_time": 182652.0,
      "text": "four letters: A, T, C and G."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182676.0,
      "end_time": 186166.0,
      "text": "And to build a human, you need three billion of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 186933.0,
      "end_time": 188112.0,
      "text": "Three billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188136.0,
      "end_time": 189715.0,
      "text": "How many are three billion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189739.0,
      "end_time": 192501.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t really make any sense as a number, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192525.0,
      "end_time": 196610.0,
      "text": "So I was thinking how I could explain myself better"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 196634.0,
      "end_time": 199684.0,
      "text": "about how big and enormous this code is."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 199708.0,
      "end_time": 202762.0,
      "text": "But there is -- I mean, I&#39;m going to have some help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202786.0,
      "end_time": 206130.0,
      "text": "and the best person to help me introduce the code"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 206370.0,
      "end_time": 209559.0,
      "text": "is actually the first man to sequence it, Dr. Craig Venter."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 209583.0,
      "end_time": 212972.0,
      "text": "So welcome onstage, Dr. Craig Venter."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212997.0,
      "end_time": 219928.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 219952.0,
      "end_time": 222208.0,
      "text": "Not the man in the flesh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 223448.0,
      "end_time": 225793.0,
      "text": "but for the first time in history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 225817.0,
      "end_time": 229279.0,
      "text": "this is the genome of a specific human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 229303.0,
      "end_time": 233630.0,
      "text": "printed page-by-page, letter-by-letter:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233870.0,
      "end_time": 237830.0,
      "text": "262,000 pages of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237107.0,
      "end_time": 241471.0,
      "text": "450 kilograms, shipped from the United States to Canada"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 241495.0,
      "end_time": 246338.0,
      "text": "thanks to Bruno Bowden, Lulu.com, a start-up, did everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246362.0,
      "end_time": 247825.0,
      "text": "It was an amazing feat."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247849.0,
      "end_time": 252146.0,
      "text": "But this is the visual perception of what is the code of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252170.0,
      "end_time": 254648.0,
      "text": "And now, for the first time, I can do something fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254672.0,
      "end_time": 257219.0,
      "text": "I can actually poke inside it and read."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257243.0,
      "end_time": 261868.0,
      "text": "So let me take an interesting book ... like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 265770.0,
      "end_time": 267611.0,
      "text": "I have an annotation; it&#39;s a fairly big book."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267635.0,
      "end_time": 271361.0,
      "text": "So just to let you see what is the code of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 272566.0,
      "end_time": 275957.0,
      "text": "Thousands and thousands and thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 275981.0,
      "end_time": 278651.0,
      "text": "and millions of letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 278675.0,
      "end_time": 281710.0,
      "text": "And they apparently make sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 281950.0,
      "end_time": 282852.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s get to a specific part."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283571.0,
      "end_time": 284933.0,
      "text": "Let me read it to you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 284957.0,
      "end_time": 285978.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286200.0,
      "end_time": 290800.0,
      "text": "\"AAG, AAT, ATA.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290965.0,
      "end_time": 293320.0,
      "text": "To you it sounds like mute letters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 293560.0,
      "end_time": 297970.0,
      "text": "but this sequence gives the color of the eyes to Craig."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297633.0,
      "end_time": 299565.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll show you another part of the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299589.0,
      "end_time": 301683.0,
      "text": "This is actually a little more complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302983.0,
      "end_time": 305630.0,
      "text": "Chromosome 14, book 132:"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305654.0,
      "end_time": 307744.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 307768.0,
      "end_time": 309440.0,
      "text": "As you might expect."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 309690.0,
      "end_time": 312535.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 314857.0,
      "end_time": 319364.0,
      "text": "\"ATT, CTT, GATT.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 320329.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "This human is lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 322400.0,
      "end_time": 326557.0,
      "text": "because if you miss just two letters in this position --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 326581.0,
      "end_time": 328458.0,
      "text": "two letters of our three billion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 328482.0,
      "end_time": 330501.0,
      "text": "he will be condemned to a terrible disease:"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 330525.0,
      "end_time": 331965.0,
      "text": "cystic fibrosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 331989.0,
      "end_time": 335402.0,
      "text": "We have no cure for it, we don&#39;t know how to solve it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 335426.0,
      "end_time": 339181.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s just two letters of difference from what we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 339585.0,
      "end_time": 342289.0,
      "text": "A wonderful book, a mighty book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 343115.0,
      "end_time": 345113.0,
      "text": "a mighty book that helped me understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 345137.0,
      "end_time": 347890.0,
      "text": "and show you something quite remarkable."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 348480.0,
      "end_time": 352915.0,
      "text": "Every one of you -- what makes me, me and you, you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352939.0,
      "end_time": 355893.0,
      "text": "is just about five million of these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 355917.0,
      "end_time": 357145.0,
      "text": "half a book."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 358150.0,
      "end_time": 359678.0,
      "text": "For the rest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 359702.0,
      "end_time": 362264.0,
      "text": "we are all absolutely identical."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 363800.0,
      "end_time": 367250.0,
      "text": "Five hundred pages is the miracle of life that you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 367500.0,
      "end_time": 369581.0,
      "text": "The rest, we all share it."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369605.0,
      "end_time": 372514.0,
      "text": "So think about that again when we think that we are different."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372538.0,
      "end_time": 374759.0,
      "text": "This is the amount that we share."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 375441.0,
      "end_time": 378869.0,
      "text": "So now that I have your attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378894.0,
      "end_time": 380253.0,
      "text": "the next question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 380277.0,
      "end_time": 381428.0,
      "text": "How do I read it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 381452.0,
      "end_time": 382961.0,
      "text": "How do I make sense out of it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 383409.0,
      "end_time": 387649.0,
      "text": "Well, for however good you can be at assembling Swedish furniture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 387673.0,
      "end_time": 391236.0,
      "text": "this instruction manual is nothing you can crack in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 392863.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392887.0,
      "end_time": 395999.0,
      "text": "And so, in 2014, two famous TEDsters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396230.0,
      "end_time": 398563.0,
      "text": "Peter Diamandis and Craig Venter himself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 398587.0,
      "end_time": 400514.0,
      "text": "decided to assemble a new company."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400538.0,
      "end_time": 401950.0,
      "text": "Human Longevity was born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 401974.0,
      "end_time": 403344.0,
      "text": "with one mission:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 403368.0,
      "end_time": 405229.0,
      "text": "trying everything we can try"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405253.0,
      "end_time": 408120.0,
      "text": "and learning everything we can learn from these books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 408360.0,
      "end_time": 409741.0,
      "text": "with one target --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 410862.0,
      "end_time": 413663.0,
      "text": "making real the dream of personalized medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 413687.0,
      "end_time": 417454.0,
      "text": "understanding what things should be done to have better health"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 417478.0,
      "end_time": 419761.0,
      "text": "and what are the secrets in these books."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 420329.0,
      "end_time": 424579.0,
      "text": "An amazing team, 40 data scientists and many, many more people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 424603.0,
      "end_time": 425953.0,
      "text": "a pleasure to work with."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 425977.0,
      "end_time": 428229.0,
      "text": "The concept is actually very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 428254.0,
      "end_time": 431412.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to use a technology called machine learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 431436.0,
      "end_time": 435974.0,
      "text": "On one side, we have genomes -- thousands of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 435999.0,
      "end_time": 439996.0,
      "text": "On the other side, we collected the biggest database of human beings:"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 440200.0,
      "end_time": 444316.0,
      "text": "phenotypes, 3D scan, NMR -- everything you can think of."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 444340.0,
      "end_time": 447239.0,
      "text": "Inside there, on these two opposite sides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 447263.0,
      "end_time": 449705.0,
      "text": "there is the secret of translation."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 449729.0,
      "end_time": 452200.0,
      "text": "And in the middle, we build a machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 452801.0,
      "end_time": 455186.0,
      "text": "We build a machine and we train a machine --"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 455210.0,
      "end_time": 458419.0,
      "text": "well, not exactly one machine, many, many machines --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 458444.0,
      "end_time": 462988.0,
      "text": "to try to understand and translate the genome in a phenotype."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 463362.0,
      "end_time": 466702.0,
      "text": "What are those letters, and what do they do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 466726.0,
      "end_time": 469473.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an approach that can be used for everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 469497.0,
      "end_time": 472490.0,
      "text": "but using it in genomics is particularly complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 472514.0,
      "end_time": 475790.0,
      "text": "Little by little we grew and we wanted to build different challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 475814.0,
      "end_time": 478546.0,
      "text": "We started from the beginning, from common traits."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 478570.0,
      "end_time": 481173.0,
      "text": "Common traits are comfortable because they are common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 481197.0,
      "end_time": 482381.0,
      "text": "everyone has them."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 482405.0,
      "end_time": 484899.0,
      "text": "So we started to ask our questions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 484923.0,
      "end_time": 486303.0,
      "text": "Can we predict height?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 486985.0,
      "end_time": 489162.0,
      "text": "Can we read the books and predict your height?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 489186.0,
      "end_time": 490337.0,
      "text": "Well, we actually can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 490361.0,
      "end_time": 492154.0,
      "text": "with five centimeters of precision."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 492178.0,
      "end_time": 495313.0,
      "text": "BMI is fairly connected to your lifestyle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 495337.0,
      "end_time": 499200.0,
      "text": "but we still can, we get in the ballpark, eight kilograms of precision."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 499225.0,
      "end_time": 500456.0,
      "text": "Can we predict eye color?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 500480.0,
      "end_time": 501638.0,
      "text": "Yeah, we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 501662.0,
      "end_time": 502986.0,
      "text": "Eighty percent accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 503466.0,
      "end_time": 505324.0,
      "text": "Can we predict skin color?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 505348.0,
      "end_time": 507789.0,
      "text": "Yeah we can, 80 percent accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 507813.0,
      "end_time": 509152.0,
      "text": "Can we predict age?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 510121.0,
      "end_time": 513860.0,
      "text": "We can, because apparently, the code changes during your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 513884.0,
      "end_time": 517166.0,
      "text": "It gets shorter, you lose pieces, it gets insertions."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 517190.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519745.00000000006,
      "text": "We read the signals, and we make a model."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 520438.0,
      "end_time": 521913.0,
      "text": "Now, an interesting challenge:"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 521937.0,
      "end_time": 523666.0,
      "text": "Can we predict a human face?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 525140.0,
      "end_time": 526292.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a little complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 526316.0,
      "end_time": 529507.0,
      "text": "because a human face is scattered among millions of these letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 529531.0,
      "end_time": 532160.0,
      "text": "And a human face is not a very well-defined object."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 532184.0,
      "end_time": 534235.0,
      "text": "So, we had to build an entire tier of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 534259.0,
      "end_time": 536969.0,
      "text": "to learn and teach a machine what a face is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 536993.0,
      "end_time": 539300.0,
      "text": "and embed and compress it."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 539540.0,
      "end_time": 541302.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re comfortable with machine learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 541326.0,
      "end_time": 543610.0,
      "text": "you understand what the challenge is here."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 544108.0,
      "end_time": 550980.0,
      "text": "Now, after 15 years -- 15 years after we read the first sequence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 550123.0,
      "end_time": 553250.0,
      "text": "this October, we started to see some signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 553490.0,
      "end_time": 555504.0,
      "text": "And it was a very emotional moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 555528.0,
      "end_time": 559273.0,
      "text": "What you see here is a subject coming in our lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 559619.0,
      "end_time": 561547.0,
      "text": "This is a face for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 561571.0,
      "end_time": 565202.0,
      "text": "So we take the real face of a subject, we reduce the complexity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 565226.0,
      "end_time": 567196.0,
      "text": "because not everything is in your face --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 567220.0,
      "end_time": 571600.0,
      "text": "lots of features and defects and asymmetries come from your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 571300.0,
      "end_time": 574499.0,
      "text": "We symmetrize the face, and we run our algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 575245.0,
      "end_time": 577143.0,
      "text": "The results that I show you right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 577167.0,
      "end_time": 580539.0,
      "text": "this is the prediction we have from the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 581596.0,
      "end_time": 583120.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 583144.0,
      "end_time": 584579.0,
      "text": "Wait a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 584603.0,
      "end_time": 589295.0,
      "text": "In these seconds, your eyes are watching, left and right, left and right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 589319.0,
      "end_time": 593248.0,
      "text": "and your brain wants those pictures to be identical."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 593273.0,
      "end_time": 595719.0,
      "text": "So I ask you to do another exercise, to be honest."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 595743.0,
      "end_time": 598300.0,
      "text": "Please search for the differences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 598540.0,
      "end_time": 599415.0,
      "text": "which are many."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 599439.0,
      "end_time": 602410.0,
      "text": "The biggest amount of signal comes from gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 602660.0,
      "end_time": 607267.0,
      "text": "then there is age, BMI, the ethnicity component of a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 607291.0,
      "end_time": 611200.0,
      "text": "And scaling up over that signal is much more complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 611260.0,
      "end_time": 614276.0,
      "text": "But what you see here, even in the differences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 614300.0,
      "end_time": 617895.0,
      "text": "lets you understand that we are in the right ballpark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 617919.0,
      "end_time": 619266.0,
      "text": "that we are getting closer."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 619291.0,
      "end_time": 621640.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s already giving you some emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 621664.0,
      "end_time": 624367.0,
      "text": "This is another subject that comes in place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 624391.0,
      "end_time": 625800.0,
      "text": "and this is a prediction."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 625824.0,
      "end_time": 630420.0,
      "text": "A little smaller face, we didn&#39;t get the complete cranial structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 630444.0,
      "end_time": 633940.0,
      "text": "but still, it&#39;s in the ballpark."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 633634.0,
      "end_time": 635858.0,
      "text": "This is a subject that comes in our lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 635882.0,
      "end_time": 637324.0,
      "text": "and this is the prediction."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 638560.0,
      "end_time": 642732.0,
      "text": "So these people have never been seen in the training of the machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 642756.0,
      "end_time": 645593.0,
      "text": "These are the so-called \"held-out\" set."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 645617.0,
      "end_time": 649357.0,
      "text": "But these are people that you will probably never believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 649381.0,
      "end_time": 652570.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re publishing everything in a scientific publication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 652810.0,
      "end_time": 653232.0,
      "text": "you can read it."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 653256.0,
      "end_time": 655600.0,
      "text": "But since we are onstage, Chris challenged me."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 655624.0,
      "end_time": 659250.0,
      "text": "I probably exposed myself and tried to predict"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 659274.0,
      "end_time": 662105.0,
      "text": "someone that you might recognize."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 662470.0,
      "end_time": 666895.0,
      "text": "So, in this vial of blood -- and believe me, you have no idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 666919.0,
      "end_time": 669799.0,
      "text": "what we had to do to have this blood now, here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 669823.0,
      "end_time": 673723.0,
      "text": "in this vial of blood is the amount of biological information"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 673748.0,
      "end_time": 676250.0,
      "text": "that we need to do a full genome sequence."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 676490.0,
      "end_time": 678119.0,
      "text": "We just need this amount."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 678528.0,
      "end_time": 681733.0,
      "text": "We ran this sequence, and I&#39;m going to do it with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 681757.0,
      "end_time": 685736.0,
      "text": "And we start to layer up all the understanding we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 685760.0,
      "end_time": 689110.0,
      "text": "In the vial of blood, we predicted he&#39;s a male."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 689134.0,
      "end_time": 690498.0,
      "text": "And the subject is a male."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 690996.0,
      "end_time": 693434.0,
      "text": "We predict that he&#39;s a meter and 76 cm."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 693458.0,
      "end_time": 695850.0,
      "text": "The subject is a meter and 77 cm."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 695874.0,
      "end_time": 699984.0,
      "text": "So, we predicted that he&#39;s 76; the subject is 82."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 700701.0,
      "end_time": 703333.0,
      "text": "We predict his age, 38."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 703357.0,
      "end_time": 705261.0,
      "text": "The subject is 35."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 705851.0,
      "end_time": 707975.0,
      "text": "We predict his eye color."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 708824.0,
      "end_time": 710350.0,
      "text": "Too dark."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 710590.0,
      "end_time": 711613.0,
      "text": "We predict his skin color."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 712260.0,
      "end_time": 713435.0,
      "text": "We are almost there."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 713899.0,
      "end_time": 715272.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s his face."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 717172.0,
      "end_time": 720441.0,
      "text": "Now, the reveal moment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 720465.0,
      "end_time": 722235.0,
      "text": "the subject is this person."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 722259.0,
      "end_time": 724194.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 724218.0,
      "end_time": 726276.0,
      "text": "And I did it intentionally."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 726300.0,
      "end_time": 729992.0,
      "text": "I am a very particular and peculiar ethnicity."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 730160.0,
      "end_time": 732966.0,
      "text": "Southern European, Italians -- they never fit in models."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 732990.0,
      "end_time": 738120.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s particular -- that ethnicity is a complex corner case for our model."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 738144.0,
      "end_time": 739653.0,
      "text": "But there is another point."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 739677.0,
      "end_time": 743154.0,
      "text": "So, one of the things that we use a lot to recognize people"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 743178.0,
      "end_time": 744900.0,
      "text": "will never be written in the genome."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 744924.0,
      "end_time": 747241.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s our free will, it&#39;s how I look."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 747265.0,
      "end_time": 750494.0,
      "text": "Not my haircut in this case, but my beard cut."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 750518.0,
      "end_time": 754710.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to show you, I&#39;m going to, in this case, transfer it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 754950.0,
      "end_time": 756860.0,
      "text": "and this is nothing more than Photoshop, no modeling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 756884.0,
      "end_time": 758597.0,
      "text": "the beard on the subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 758621.0,
      "end_time": 762930.0,
      "text": "And immediately, we get much, much better in the feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 762955.0,
      "end_time": 765664.0,
      "text": "So, why do we do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 767938.0,
      "end_time": 773780.0,
      "text": "We certainly don&#39;t do it for predicting height"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 773102.0,
      "end_time": 775473.0,
      "text": "or taking a beautiful picture out of your blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 776390.0,
      "end_time": 780408.0,
      "text": "We do it because the same technology and the same approach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 780432.0,
      "end_time": 782952.0,
      "text": "the machine learning of this code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 782976.0,
      "end_time": 786113.0,
      "text": "is helping us to understand how we work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 786137.0,
      "end_time": 787622.0,
      "text": "how your body works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 787647.0,
      "end_time": 789312.0,
      "text": "how your body ages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 789336.0,
      "end_time": 792105.0,
      "text": "how disease generates in your body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 792129.0,
      "end_time": 795101.0,
      "text": "how your cancer grows and develops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 795125.0,
      "end_time": 796908.0,
      "text": "how drugs work"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 796932.0,
      "end_time": 799246.0,
      "text": "and if they work on your body."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 799713.0,
      "end_time": 801380.0,
      "text": "This is a huge challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 801894.0,
      "end_time": 803532.0,
      "text": "This is a challenge that we share"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 803556.0,
      "end_time": 806135.0,
      "text": "with thousands of other researchers around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 806159.0,
      "end_time": 808381.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called personalized medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 809125.0,
      "end_time": 812585.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the ability to move from a statistical approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 812609.0,
      "end_time": 814641.0,
      "text": "where you&#39;re a dot in the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 814665.0,
      "end_time": 816478.0,
      "text": "to a personalized approach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 816502.0,
      "end_time": 818686.0,
      "text": "where we read all these books"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 818711.0,
      "end_time": 821575.0,
      "text": "and we get an understanding of exactly how you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 822260.0,
      "end_time": 825622.0,
      "text": "But it is a particularly complicated challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 825646.0,
      "end_time": 829644.0,
      "text": "because of all these books, as of today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 829668.0,
      "end_time": 832310.0,
      "text": "we just know probably two percent:"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 833270.0,
      "end_time": 836680.0,
      "text": "four books of more than 175."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 838210.0,
      "end_time": 841227.0,
      "text": "And this is not the topic of my talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 842145.0,
      "end_time": 844742.0,
      "text": "because we will learn more."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 845378.0,
      "end_time": 848470.0,
      "text": "There are the best minds in the world on this topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 849480.0,
      "end_time": 850882.0,
      "text": "The prediction will get better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 850906.0,
      "end_time": 853159.0,
      "text": "the model will get more precise."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 853183.0,
      "end_time": 855400.0,
      "text": "And the more we learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 855650.0,
      "end_time": 859895.0,
      "text": "the more we will be confronted with decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 859919.0,
      "end_time": 862939.0,
      "text": "that we never had to face before"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 862964.0,
      "end_time": 864399.0,
      "text": "about life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 864423.0,
      "end_time": 866970.0,
      "text": "about death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 866121.0,
      "end_time": 867723.0,
      "text": "about parenting."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 872626.0,
      "end_time": 877372.0,
      "text": "So, we are touching the very inner detail on how life works."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 878118.0,
      "end_time": 881276.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a revolution that cannot be confined"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 881300.0,
      "end_time": 883959.0,
      "text": "in the domain of science or technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 884960.0,
      "end_time": 887204.0,
      "text": "This must be a global conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 887798.0,
      "end_time": 893150.0,
      "text": "We must start to think of the future we&#39;re building as a humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 893390.0,
      "end_time": 897103.0,
      "text": "We need to interact with creatives, with artists, with philosophers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 897127.0,
      "end_time": 898637.0,
      "text": "with politicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 898661.0,
      "end_time": 899819.0,
      "text": "Everyone is involved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 899843.0,
      "end_time": 902668.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the future of our species."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 903273.0,
      "end_time": 907241.0,
      "text": "Without fear, but with the understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 907265.0,
      "end_time": 911136.0,
      "text": "that the decisions that we make in the next year"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 911160.0,
      "end_time": 914949.0,
      "text": "will change the course of history forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 915732.0,
      "end_time": 916891.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 916916.0,
      "end_time": 927750.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}